<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>   If EQ wasn't designed to be addictive, why would people spend 36 hours straight camping items? How many PS2 gamers play that long against a computer opponent in one sitting?<br>
